                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">First off, CONGRATS!!  We are proud of you even if you don't really feel it yourself.  You can't beat yourself up for how memory always seems brighter than the present tense.  That's just how nostalgia works <img src="images/smiles/icon_sad.gif" alt="icon_sad.gif" border="0" />.
